\subsection{Strengths and Limitations}

Strengths include standardized comparison across models, broad domain coverage, and ease of automated evaluation. Key limitations include: (1)~rapid saturation as models improve, (2)~vulnerability to benchmark contamination~\cite{yang2023rethinking}, (3)~multiple-choice format artificially constraining evaluation to recognition rather than generation, and (4)~static nature preventing evaluation of evolving capabilities.

