\textbf{DecodingTrust}~\cite{wang2023decodingtrust} provides comprehensive trustworthiness evaluation across 8 dimensions: toxicity, stereotype bias, adversarial robustness, out-of-distribution robustness, privacy, machine ethics, fairness, and hallucination.

